{"type": "article", "id": 35919, "title": "看图：这里是过去24小时内发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。PS：我们认为这个世界的重要性不应该有绝对的等级，重点是看得更多，探索更多。", "date": "2016-12-23T02:58:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 5, "author": 1218, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161223110024niD932SOIuMNweBF.jpg", "contents": "<h3>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h3><p class=\"\">1.&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>武装分子袭击阿富汗国会议员住所</b></span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223102040jlBCPsHYxhTpQaVe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; @视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">阿富汗喀布尔，清理房间的男子通过玻璃上的弹孔看向屋外。喀布尔一位议员的住宅 21 日晚遭到袭击，造成包括 3 名袭击者在内的 11 人死亡。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>2. &nbsp;澳大利亚挫败圣诞节恐袭阴谋&nbsp;</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223104523RufIyz4jrVlDw5dv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; @视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">澳大利亚悉尼，澳大利亚总理特恩布尔就恐袭事件出席新闻发布会。当日澳大利亚警方挫败一起针对墨尔本中部地区的恐怖袭击阴谋，并在墨尔本展开的突击行动中逮捕了七人。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>3. &nbsp;第一条太阳能道路</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223081833nW84txu6VOs0gpHc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">法国图鲁夫尔，法国建造的全世界第一条太阳能道路举行了揭幕仪式。这条道路的路面铺设太阳能板，可随时储存能源，可供 500 万人用电量。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>4. &nbsp;雾霾转移到了上海</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223103254M8okRmeCGs6A4rBx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">上海，截止今早 8 时，实时空气质量 AQI 指数达 223，霾黄色预警和空气重污染蓝色预警高挂。图为今日早间在外滩景观平台上看到的浦江两岸。&nbsp;<br></p><h3>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h3><p class=\"\"><b>1. &nbsp;夏日圣诞节</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223104838xZ6pDfHqmgNL8bPa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">澳大利亚墨尔本，圣诞节的南半球正值夏日，虽然少了雪和炉火，但圣诞气氛也很浓，夏装圣诞帽是标准装束。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>2. 查尔斯王子的针线作品</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612231057149ECacl6YNqsipK8g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">英国格洛斯特郡，查尔斯王子在探访英格兰切尔滕纳姆医院时，拿起针线缝起圣诞雪人装饰物。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>3. &nbsp;枕头大战</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223082021e3qQFRPcYd7EgTxs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">捷克布拉格老城广场举行枕头大战。约有 100 多人参加了这场历时 3-4 分钟的“枕头大战”。</p><p class=\"\"><b>4. 手绘 3D 宿舍</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016122310533358yTaOo9IjzJPXrK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@视觉中国&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><p>浙江宁波，浙江纺织服装职业技术学院大一学生陈先权通过手绘 3D 画，5 天内让寝室变了个样。&nbsp;</p>"}